title: 2016 Chevrolet Camaro SS 6.2L V8 with Magnaflow Cat-Back Exhaust
description: MagnaFlow's Cat-Back exhaust system for the 2016 Chevrolet Camaro SS 6.2L features polished stainless steel construction and includes a lifetime warranty. Functionality of the stock exhaust valves has been seamlessly integrated for full control over your driving experience.
